<concept id="2bc8b56b764a22a035878f5c748e0046" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/">
  <title>View Authentication Parameters</title>
  <prolog>
    <source/>
    <permissions view="ericsson_internal"/>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta content="NA" name="workitem"/>
    </metadata>
    <resourceid id="NA" ux-source-priority="topic-and-map"/>
  </prolog>
  <conbody>
    <p>To list all the configuration information for the system, run the
following command from node-1 or node-2:</p>
    <p>
      <systemoutput>$</systemoutput>
      <userinput>bootloader.py config list --show_all</userinput>
    </p>
    <p>Then find the authentication parameters in <filepath>tomcat</filepath> section.</p>
    <p> The <cite>Authentication Parameters Table</cite> lists all the parameters for authentication
      configuration.</p>
    <table colsep="1" id="tbPsw" rowsep="1">
      <title>Authentication Parameters</title>
      <tgroup cols="4">
        <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="180.67pt"/>
        <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="179.40pt"/>
        <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="87.10pt"/>
        <colspec colname="col4" colwidth="55.71pt"/>
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Parameter</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Description</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Type</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Default Value</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MIN_PASSWD_LENGTH</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Minimum password length <fn>The password
length must consist of minimum 12 characters.</fn>
              </p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>12</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MIN_DIGIT_CHARS</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Minimum number of digits [0-9] within a password</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>1</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MIN_UPPER_CASE_CHARS</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Minimum number of upper case characters [A-Z] within a password</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>1</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MIN_LOWER_CASE_CHARS</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Minimum number of lower case characters [a-z] within a password</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>1</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MIN_SPECIAL_CHARS</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Minimum number of special characters
                  <filepath>[!"#$%&amp;'()*+,-./:;&lt;=>?@[\]^_`{|}~]</filepath> within a
                password</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>1</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MAX_DAYS_TO_REMEMBER</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Number of days that a password cannot be
reused</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>365</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MAX_DAYS_TO_LIVE</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Maximum days before a password needs to
be changed</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>90</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_MAX_LOGIN_ATTEMPTS</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Maximum number of failed login attempts
before the user is locked out</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>3</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_BRUTE_FORCE_INITIAL_LOCK_PERIOD</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Initial locking period (in milliseconds)
of default <filepath>admin</filepath> GUI user after reaching "AUTHN_MAX_LOGIN_ATTEMPTS"</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>5000</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>AUTHN_BRUTE_FORCE_MAX_LOCK_PERIOD</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Maximum locking period (in milliseconds)
for the default <filepath>admin</filepath> GUI user.</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>Integer</p>
            </entry>
            <entry valign="middle">
              <p>900000</p>
            </entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
